    <h2 class="title"> Applying for the NMC Virtual Learning Prize </h2>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Download the <a href="http://web.nmc.org/files/virtual-learning-prize-app.doc" class="doc">Virtual Learning Prize application form</a>, complete the information, and email to <a href="mailto:virtual-learning@nmc.org">virtual-learning@nmc.org</a>.</p>
<div align="center"><a href="http://web.nmc.org/files/virtual-learning-prize-app.doc"><img src="/images/virtual-learning-prize-app.png" alt ="" /></a></div>
